    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It's in really great shape and has been super well-cared for\u2014perfect for someone looking for a smooth, worry-free ride. It\u2019s clean, drives like a dream, and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
