    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via eight individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,400 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. The suspension geometry features a double-joint spring strut front axle and a five-link rear setup, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for optimized lateral dynamics. Maintained with an emphasis on performance integrity, including recent service to the cooling system and VANOS solenoids. A true driver's machine with a linear power band and communicative hydraulic steering.",
